title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show JAN-30-2014 THURS
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show JAN-30-2014 THURS..........PODCAST




The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET


       
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 1/30/14Thursday, January 30, 2014 




The Federal Government is scamming you,
      in more ways than one, and Glenn lays it out. 

     Also, a very special guest joins the show;
          Captain Sam Brown, a veteran of the war in Afghanistan,
               is running for the Texas Statehouse,
                   and Glenn wants you to hear his remarkable story.

      Plus, Mark Levin's email to Glenn, the Right attacking Ted Cruz,

      Senator Mike Lee takes on Attorney General Eric Holder, and much more.
